            <doc:para>
              An array of codecs descriptors from <doc:tt>pk-gstreamer-install</doc:tt>, e.g.
              <doc:tt>Advanced Streaming Format (ASF) demuxer|decoder-video/x-ms-asf</doc:tt>
            </doc:para>
